# ===========================================================================
# FRONTEND env — copy this file to `.env.local` (project root).
# Next.js only auto-loads `.env*` files from the project root.
#
# These NEXT_PUBLIC_* values are inlined into the BROWSER bundle at build time,
# so they are public by definition. Backend secrets live in `supabase/.env`
# instead — see `supabase/.env.example`.
# ===========================================================================

